<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.164567>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 2. 1, Holotype male Pamexis hantam n. sp. (Forewing length 29.9 mm); 2, Paratype male P. namaqua Mansell (Forewing length 24.3 mm). Photos: M. W. Mansell ©" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/164567/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.164568>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3 – 5. Pamexis hantam n. sp. Resting position on lichen background. Photos: R. W. Mansell ©" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/164568/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.164575>
    dc:description "FIGURE 27. Distribution of Pamexis species." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/164575/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.260846>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 10. Pamexis hantam n. sp. Showing variability in wing markings, female specimens. Photos: M. W. Mansell ©" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/260846/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.260849>
    dc:description "FIGURES 22 – 26. 22, Pamexis hantam n. sp. Female Terminalia, Pregenitalae. Ga = Anterior gonapophyses, Prg = Pregenitale. 23, Pamexis namaqua, Thorax and abdomen male; 24, female; 25, Pamexis hantam Thorax and abdomen male; 26, female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/260849/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.164571>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11 – 13. Pamexis hantam n. sp. Male Terminalia. 11, lateral; 12, dorsal; 13, ventral. Epr = Ectoproct, T 9 = Tergite 9, IX = Sternite 9, Pa = Parameres." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/164571/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.260847>
    dc:description "FIGURES 14 – 19. Pamexis hantam n. sp. Male Genitalia. 14, Gonarcus & Parameres complex dorsal; 15, ventral; 16, lateral; 17, Hypandrium internum dorsal; 18, lateral; 19, ventral. Gb = Gonarcal bulla, Gs = Gonarcus, Pa = Parameres." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/260847/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.260848>
    dc:description "FIGURES 20 – 21. Pamexis hantam n. sp. Female Terminalia. 20, Lateral. Note: paired ectoprocts. 21, Spermatheca. Epr = Ectoprocts, Ga = Anterior gonapophyses, Gl = Lateral gonapophyses, Spt = Spermatheca." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/260848/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

